{"tha-ap124:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap124:0.2":"Sereyyavagga ","tha-ap124:0.3":"Pupphathupiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap124:1.1":"“Himavantassavidure, ","tha-ap124:1.2":"kukkuro nama pabbato; ","tha-ap124:1.3":"Vemajjhe tassa vasati, ","tha-ap124:1.4":"brahmano mantaparagu. ","tha-ap124:2.1":"Panca sissasahassani, ","tha-ap124:2.2":"parivarenti mam sada; ","tha-ap124:2.3":"Pubbutthayi ca te asum, ","tha-ap124:2.4":"mantesu ca visarada. ","tha-ap124:3.1":"Buddho loke samuppanno, ","tha-ap124:3.2":"tam vijanatha no bhavam; ","tha-ap124:3.3":"Asitibyanjananassa, ","tha-ap124:3.4":"battimsavaralakkhana. ","tha-ap124:4.1":"Byamappabho jinavaro, ","tha-ap124:4.2":"adiccova virocati; ","tha-ap124:4.3":"Sissanam vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap124:4.4":"brahmano mantaparagu. ","tha-ap124:5.1":"Assama abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap124:5.2":"disam pucchati sissake; ","tha-ap124:5.3":"Yamhi dese mahaviro, ","tha-ap124:5.4":"vasati lokanayako. ","tha-ap124:6.1":"Taham disam namassissam, ","tha-ap124:6.2":"jinam appatipuggalam; ","tha-ap124:6.3":"Udaggacitto sumano, ","tha-ap124:6.4":"pujesim tam tathagatam. ","tha-ap124:7.1":"Etha sissa gamissama, ","tha-ap124:7.2":"dakkhissama tathagatam; ","tha-ap124:7.3":"Vanditva satthuno pade, ","tha-ap124:7.4":"sossama jinasasanam. ","tha-ap124:8.1":"Ekaham abhinikkhamma, ","tha-ap124:8.2":"byadhim patilabhim aham; ","tha-ap124:8.3":"Byadhina pilito santo, ","tha-ap124:8.4":"salam vasayitum gamim. ","tha-ap124:9.1":"Sabbe sisse samanetva, ","tha-ap124:9.2":"apucchim te tathagatam; ","tha-ap124:9.3":"Kidisam lokanathassa, ","tha-ap124:9.4":"gunam paramabuddhino. ","tha-ap124:10.1":"Te me puttha viyakamsu, ","tha-ap124:10.2":"Yatha dassavino tatha; ","tha-ap124:10.3":"Sakkaccam buddhasettham tam, ","tha-ap124:10.4":"Desesum mama sammukha. ","tha-ap124:11.1":"Tesaham vacanam sutva, ","tha-ap124:11.2":"sakam cittam pasadayim; ","tha-ap124:11.3":"Pupphehi thupam katvana, ","tha-ap124:11.4":"tattha kalankato aham. ","tha-ap124:12.1":"Te me sariram jhapetva, ","tha-ap124:12.2":"agamum buddhasantikam; ","tha-ap124:12.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap124:12.4":"sattharamabhivadayum. ","tha-ap124:13.1":"Pupphehi thupam katvana, ","tha-ap124:13.2":"sugatassa mahesino; ","tha-ap124:13.3":"Kappanam satasahassam, ","tha-ap124:13.4":"duggatim nupapajjaham. ","tha-ap124:14.1":"Cattalisasahassamhi, ","tha-ap124:14.2":"kappe solasa khattiya; ","tha-ap124:14.3":"Namenaggisama nama, ","tha-ap124:14.4":"cakkavatti mahabbala. ","tha-ap124:15.1":"Visakappasahassamhi, ","tha-ap124:15.2":"rajano cakkavattino; ","tha-ap124:15.3":"Ghatasanasanamava, ","tha-ap124:15.4":"atthattimsa mahipati. ","tha-ap124:16.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap124:16.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap124:16.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap124:17.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pupphathupiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap124:18.1":"Pupphathupiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}